high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to the sink.
Pick up the head of lettuce from inside the sink.
Turn around and hang a left at the wall to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the lettuce on the second shelf from the top, let it chill for seven seconds, remove the lettuce and close the door.
Turn around and hang a right at the stove to return to the sink.
Put the lettuce into the left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce in a sink.

high_descs: Pick up lettuce out of right sink from behind the knife.
Turn around, proceed to refrigerator, turn left to face refrigerator.
Place lettuce on second shelf down, close fridge.  Wait five seconds, open refrigerator and remove lettuce.
Turn left and proceed to sink.
Put lettuce in left sink behind the fork.
anns.task_desc: Move lettuce to fridge to cool, then move it to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the head of lettuce out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to the refrigerator on the left.
Put the head of lettuce in the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk back to the sink.
Put the head of lettuce in the sink basin on the left.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled head of lettuce in a sink basin.
